The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                               Good Morning
      Hello It's Wednesday , March 11 , 2009                    
	Holi     Katha, Kirtan and Maha-abhishek at Iskcon House, 22 Gurusaday Road, 5.30pm.    
	Guidelines    Dont move around in trucks and Matadors with colours.     Dont throw colours at people unwilling to play and police and army personnel.    Dont splash colours from the rooftops or balconies. Offenders may be arrested.    Dont throw colours at people of other religious communities.    Dont mix harmful chemicals with colours.    Dont consume liquor in open spaces and create nuisance in public.    Using loudspeakers is banned by the high court because of the forthcoming HS exams.     Inform police if there is any rowdyism in the locality.     
	Multiplex    INOX Swabhumi will open at 2pm.    INOX Forum at 4pm.    INOX City Centre at 6pm.    Fame (South City Mall) at 5pm.    Fame (Hiland Park) at 4.30pm.    
	Art watch    An exhibition of paintings by Dhiraj Choudhury at The Stadel, 11am to 8pm.     The Rhythm of Colour at Idiyas Gallery, 10.30am to 7pm.                                                                                                                                                                   
